ASL FontRequester Tags
======================

Usage: AllocAslRequest_/AslRequest_

ASLFO_Flags: ( ti_Tag = $80080014 )

"OR" together the following flags in ti_Data:

FOF_DOFRONTPEN     ( = $ 1 )
FOF_DOBACKPEN      ( = $ 2 )
FOF_DOSTYLE        ( = $ 4 )
FOF_DODRAWMODE     ( = $ 8 )
FOF_FIXEDWIDTHONLY ( = $10 )
FOF_PRIVATEIDCMP   ( = $20 )
FOF_INTUIFUNC      ( = $40 )
FOF_FILTERFUNC     ( = $80 )

See the Tag equivalents for descriptions.


